Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.37,0:00:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流動的水沒有形狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.98,0:00:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂流的風找不到蹤迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.63,0:00:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何案件的推理都取決于心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.77,0:00:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花語意味深長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.38,0:00:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌曲 殺意都跨越時空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.62,0:00:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.23,0:00:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 頭腦卻是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.03,0:00:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.76,0:00:21.64,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,35)}{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}正因爲妳和我是不同的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.87,0:00:30.61,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}喜好不同 腳程與表達的方式也大異其趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.37,0:00:37.54,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}如今我們在兩人的記憶中正在漸漸褪色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.31,0:00:45.04,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(60,0)}{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}我摸索過 卻開始探尋其他人與未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.17,0:00:52.19,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}我比自己想象的活得更堅強 追尋一種特別的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.33,0:00:56.17,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}爲難以應付的每一天所苦惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.37,0:00:59.43,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx129}ture heart for mystery eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.59,0:01:06.97,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}爲了不再迷惑 請別松開妳的手腕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.20,0:01:09.87,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(30,40)}{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}即使是互相傷害的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.97,0:01:21.32,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}我只是一直在迷惘的時空中找尋答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.59,0:01:27.85,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,800)}{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}朝著下一個舞台  {\fscx132}you take your way
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.37,0:01:32.17,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,800)}{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}請抱緊我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.29,0:01:39.29,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,730)}{\fs20}{\fscx101}I feel so all in secret life
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.14,0:01:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們受加那娛樂集團會長加那善則之托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.37,0:01:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出席晚會並保護她的妻子美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.37,0:01:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn宋体}{\fs24}{\pos(476,465)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.68,0:01:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她近來受到什麽人的騷擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.32,0:02:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚會中途 突然停電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.72,0:02:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲在她自己的房間裏被人襲擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.72,0:02:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn宋体}{\fs24}{\pos(188,465)}{\shade1}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.87,0:02:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都懷疑犯人就是晚會的主角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.97,0:02:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑拉爾天馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.07,0:02:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.27,0:02:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊接著傑拉爾天馬就被人殺害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.37,0:02:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色殺意的夜想曲（後篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.17,0:02:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶器是騎士的劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.47,0:02:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼琴調音用的音叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.87,0:02:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傷痕是什麽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.19,0:02:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 琴凳爲什麽在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.15,0:02:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓在大沙發下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.62,0:02:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要到處亂走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.72,0:02:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位 爲了保護現場請大家都去休憩室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.42,0:02:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑拉爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.22,0:03:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善則先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.47,0:03:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺害天馬的是妳麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.42,0:03:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.72,0:03:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在休憩室 就是這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.27,0:03:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬根本不理我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.17,0:03:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人走到鋼琴那邊去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.37,0:03:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 我正想在這坐下的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.62,0:03:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到“嘶”的響聲和慘叫 跑過去一看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.47,0:03:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.12,0:03:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是當時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.97,0:03:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的人都在一樓大廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.57,0:03:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.82,0:03:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夠嗆 妳幹了什麽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.12,0:03:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了 不是我幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.42,0:03:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.72,0:03:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我獨斷決定的這件事 妳心裏就覺得不滿意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.42,0:03:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才妳又得知 天馬和嫂子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.87,0:03:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前戀愛過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.37,0:03:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就激動起來了 不是麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.77,0:03:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.77,0:03:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在他就是支持妳也晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.09,0:03:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾 會長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.97,0:04:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 控制加那娛樂集團的變成誰了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.55,0:04:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是無辜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.37,0:04:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看見犯人了麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.42,0:04:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑到這裏來的時候已經空無一人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.95,0:04:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才美咲帶我們來參觀的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.95,0:04:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn宋体}{\fs24}{\pos(248,465)}{\shade1}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.60,0:04:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼琴蓋是蓋著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.95,0:04:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是傑拉爾打開的麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.42,0:04:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以這個房間的大小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.88,0:04:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不打開蓋 琴聲也足夠響了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.62,0:04:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑拉爾沒有必要打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.52,0:04:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.77,0:04:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬進這個房間之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.02,0:04:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼琴的蓋子是打開的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.02,0:04:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以這樣設想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.87,0:04:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人在殺人時 爲了讓別人從這邊看不到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.40,0:04:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以預先把蓋子打開的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.85,0:05:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個房間的出口只有通往休憩室的那扇門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.15,0:05:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗戶雖然開了一扇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.26,0:05:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是下面是海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.45,0:05:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是跳下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.76,0:05:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也很難避開礁石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.09,0:05:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個窗台上也有傷痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.68,0:05:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是被繩子之類的東西勒過的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.65,0:05:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和美咲被襲擊的時候留下的痕迹一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.65,0:05:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn宋体}{\fs24}{\pos(188,465)}{\shade1}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.29,0:05:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有根繩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.63,0:05:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從上從下都可以逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.29,0:05:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有這種可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.85,0:05:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是能在這麽短的時間內逃走麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.41,0:05:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地板上留下的劍尖的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.05,0:05:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是垂直于地面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.13,0:05:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.89,0:05:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.83,0:06:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.62,0:06:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整理一下案發當時各位所在的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.36,0:06:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位請去隔壁的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.63,0:06:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊這個小吊燈的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.04,0:06:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比那邊那個大吊燈的位置高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.95,0:06:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲帶我們來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.95,0:06:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn宋体}{\fs24}{\pos(248,465)}{\shade1}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.48,0:06:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是在更低的位置上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.39,0:06:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏也有痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.10,0:06:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和窗台上的痕迹一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.90,0:06:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調節吊燈高低的就是這個手柄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.68,0:06:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很容易就可以轉動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.90,0:06:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這個盒子上沒有灰塵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.13,0:06:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色愛的夜想曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.33,0:07:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那首歌是10年前天馬送給美咲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.33,0:07:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn宋体}{\fs24}{\pos(452,465)}{\shade1}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.03,0:07:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.46,0:07:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣的話就怎麽樣了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.83,0:07:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.43,0:07:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.90,0:07:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是血麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.98,0:07:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.13,0:07:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼琴的裏面也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.73,0:07:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小林警探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.88,0:07:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什魅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.51,0:07:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.43,0:07:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警長說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.63,0:07:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我去找貝多芬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是在海裏麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.93,0:07:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.03,0:07:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何 善則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.88,0:07:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請跟我回警署
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.73,0:07:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.08,0:08:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說多少遍妳才會相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.26,0:08:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲 救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.26,0:08:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn宋体}{\fs24}{\pos(290,465)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.16,0:08:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咾公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.36,0:08:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.48,0:08:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和那個地方對得上的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.84,0:08:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.30,0:08:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裏掉下來的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.96,0:08:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個裝飾品的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.08,0:08:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人只可能是那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.89,0:08:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.02,0:08:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司我會照應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.71,0:08:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是要趕緊出個傑拉爾天馬的追悼版吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.14,0:08:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.19,0:08:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個就是襲擊美咲的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.19,0:08:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn宋体}{\fs24}{\pos(380,465)}{\shad1}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.98,0:08:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.36,0:08:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如妳所說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.28,0:08:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下面的海岸上找到了貝多芬像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.29,0:08:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒叫妳去找啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.79,0:08:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.99,0:08:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.88,0:09:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扶手下面留有好像是細繩之類的勒出來的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.06,0:09:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.07,0:09:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是什麽線啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.43,0:09:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是釣魚的時候用的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.34,0:09:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是魚線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.88,0:09:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.88,0:09:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個雕像上還帶著魚線和這個棒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.04,0:09:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.40,0:09:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.38,0:09:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扶手上的傷痕是魚線勒出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.93,0:09:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推理的不錯 就這麽繼續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.03,0:09:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 爲什麽用貝多芬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.11,0:09:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 這上面也有貝多芬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.16,0:09:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.46,0:09:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是昨晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.63,0:09:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在這房間偷拍的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.43,0:09:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好是那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.67,0:09:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 貝多芬像沒有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.51,0:09:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.51,0:09:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿披風的外國人是怎麽來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.41,0:09:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.60,0:09:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝多芬就是這個房間裏的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.46,0:10:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要做這個機關的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.68,0:10:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不覺得那裏的寬度應該和棒的長度相同麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.43,0:10:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那裏缺的一塊就是剛才的碎片吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.44,0:10:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.41,0:10:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那邊的陽台上試一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.29,0:10:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲 有魚竿的話借我用一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.29,0:10:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn宋体}{\fs24}{\pos(206,465)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.39,0:10:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.33,0:10:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽台的頂棚比扶手向外伸的更遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.88,0:10:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用魚竿就簡單了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.89,0:10:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把線的一頭系成環 上面綴個東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.95,0:10:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是爲了穿過來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.89,0:10:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繩子穿過扶手下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.99,0:10:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小林警探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.15,0:10:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著魚線的環 把手指伸進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.19,0:10:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.83,0:10:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警長能不能把大衣借我用一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.25,0:10:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 准備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.73,0:10:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小林警探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.17,0:10:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請和犯人扭打 按照我的指示放手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.67,0:11:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉繩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.47,0:11:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.17,0:11:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.67,0:11:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.32,0:11:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在放手 拉繩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.77,0:11:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開繩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.07,0:11:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起 完美極了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.22,0:11:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我的大衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.17,0:11:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這情景和美咲被襲擊的時候一模一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.17,0:11:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn宋体}{\fs24}{\pos(260,465)}{\shad1}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 嫂子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.37,0:11:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗的房間裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.87,0:11:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著就象穿披風的外國人逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.67,0:11:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 加害者和被害者就是同一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.47,0:11:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她拉掉樓下的電閘 立刻跑進房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.77,0:11:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖上門開始呼救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.22,0:12:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧 美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.22,0:12:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn宋体}{\fs24}{\pos(386,465)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.67,0:12:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.67,0:12:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn宋体}{\fs24}{\pos(332,465)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.62,0:12:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推理的很出色 不愧是名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.77,0:12:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那些騷擾 恐嚇信都是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.67,0:12:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是唏朢妳能相信 所以才演了這麽一出戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.57,0:12:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.07,0:12:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這個事和天馬被殺沒有直接關系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.67,0:12:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善則 請跟我走一趟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.67,0:12:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.47,0:12:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽下去可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.87,0:12:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什魅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.77,0:12:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鋼琴室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.67,0:12:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 出什魅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.57,0:12:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.27,0:13:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次又怎麽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.07,0:13:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警長 先別把他帶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.17,0:13:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.87,0:13:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要做推理演出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.67,0:13:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 警長 我終于弄明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.17,0:13:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請妳看看地板上的那個傷痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.27,0:13:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷痕的角度是垂直于地面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.87,0:13:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢查的結果也是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.47,0:13:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 窗台和回廊的扶手上的傷痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.77,0:13:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬手上拿的音叉上的傷痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.67,0:13:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這些傷痕聯系起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.77,0:13:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就構成了一個非常恐怖的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.47,0:13:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個地板上的傷痕的正上方有個吊燈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.47,0:13:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個吊燈也就是連接這些傷痕的最後一環
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.77,0:13:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難 難道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.47,0:13:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.67,0:13:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吊在那個吊燈上的劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.97,0:13:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垂直的掉落下來 穿透天馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.17,0:13:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在地板上留下了垂直地面的傷痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.47,0:13:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.77,0:14:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.27,0:14:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他正巧站在劍落下的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.97,0:14:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍也應該是刺在頭上或者肩上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.87,0:14:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是天馬當時是臉朝下的姿勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.87,0:14:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽可能是這個姿勢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.37,0:14:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音叉可以解開這個謎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.37,0:14:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.67,0:14:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有琴凳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.27,0:14:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼琴和琴凳之間的距離只有一人寬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.87,0:14:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.67,0:14:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬走到琴鍵前面准備彈琴的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.97,0:14:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現琴凳倒在鋼琴邊上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.37,0:14:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且調音用的音叉也掉在地上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.67,0:14:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 天馬就去撿音叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.17,0:14:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 這樣的話就是背對著劍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.57,0:14:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是那個撿起來的音叉使劍落下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.57,0:14:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.47,0:14:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個恐怖的機關是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.37,0:15:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把劍挂在長繩的中央
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.07,0:15:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個繩頭一起穿過吊燈的輪子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.67,0:15:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再繞過回廊的扶手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.97,0:15:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一頭在大沙發上繞幾圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.67,0:15:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,線頭系在音叉上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.27,0:15:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一頭 從窗戶扔出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.17,0:15:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面懸挂著重物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.67,0:15:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 只要等天馬去撿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.37,0:15:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓在椅子腿下面的音叉就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.37,0:15:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍的重量使音叉上系的繩被拉脫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.47,0:15:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沈重的劍就在一瞬間落下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.67,0:15:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 系在劍上的魚線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.17,0:15:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被窗外挂著的重物拉著落下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.97,0:15:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就消失在海裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.47,0:15:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.17,0:15:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽犯人是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.12,0:15:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回想一下 使用魚線做的機關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.07,0:16:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用重物將證據帶入大海的這個方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.87,0:16:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和剛才那個穿披風的外國人的手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.77,0:16:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是非常相像麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.47,0:16:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.47,0:16:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn宋体}{\fs24}{\pos(332,465)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.17,0:16:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 犯人就是妳 美咲小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.17,0:16:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn宋体}{\fs24}{\pos(404,465)}{\shad1}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.77,0:16:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在給所有人倒上酒之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.07,0:16:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝作是去了廚房 其實是在這裏做手腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.67,0:16:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把吊燈吊到最高點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.07,0:16:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣劍就不容易被發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.07,0:16:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還能夠提高殺傷力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.77,0:16:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來認爲妳是名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.47,0:16:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實只是徒有虛名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.37,0:16:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有證據證明是我做的麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.87,0:16:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 請看看鋼琴的蓋子上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.87,0:16:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和裏面沾上的汙漬吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.97,0:16:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是 酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.47,0:16:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒沾在鋼琴的那個位置上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.67,0:16:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明是在打開蓋的時候掉落在那裏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.67,0:17:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠讓酒掉在那裏的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.97,0:17:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.37,0:17:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽這麽肯定呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.57,0:17:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲米歇爾從法國帶來的酒是獨一無貳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.87,0:17:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這就是我的酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.27,0:17:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那酒大家都喝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.47,0:17:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒喝的只有妳 美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.47,0:17:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn宋体}{\fs24}{\pos(410,465)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.07,0:17:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不小心撞到妳 把酒灑在妳身上的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.57,0:17:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計是當時留在妳胸花上的酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.47,0:17:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在妳打開鋼琴蓋的時候掉下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.27,0:17:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳做了很多假象僞裝天馬騷擾妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.27,0:17:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還把舊照片放在容易被發現的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.47,0:17:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以激起善則的怒氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.37,0:17:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好讓他替妳擔起殺害天馬的罪名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.67,0:17:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲 是真的麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.67,0:17:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn宋体}{\fs24}{\pos(278,465)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.47,0:17:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽妳怎麽解釋剛才有人襲擊她的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.27,0:18:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是她自導自演的戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.17,0:18:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個恐嚇電話也是美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.17,0:18:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn宋体}{\fs24}{\pos(428,465)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.87,0:18:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷的從自己的手機上給自己打的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.87,0:18:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫂子爲什麽要殺天馬呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.07,0:18:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才找到的天馬和美咲的照片上的日期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.07,0:18:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn宋体}{\fs24}{\pos(344,465)}{\shad1}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.17,0:18:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美咲結婚短短半年之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.17,0:18:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn宋体}{\fs24}{\pos(248,465)}{\shad1}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.97,0:18:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.07,0:18:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 紅色愛的夜想曲也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.87,0:18:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前天馬送給妳的歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.37,0:18:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這首歌看上去像是首情歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.87,0:18:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 根據花語來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.67,0:18:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅玫瑰代表熱情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.37,0:18:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金盞花代表絕朢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.87,0:18:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半邊蓮代表惡意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.27,0:18:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有大理花代表背叛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.47,0:18:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 這首歌表達的其實是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.87,0:18:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對背叛自己的愛人的仇恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.47,0:18:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣麽 美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.47,0:18:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn宋体}{\fs24}{\pos(386,465)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.27,0:18:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 10年前的那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.97,0:19:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說無論如何都無法離開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.27,0:19:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把他約到附近的海岸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.87,0:19:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他推了下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.47,0:19:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後妳就和善則結婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.17,0:19:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是天馬因爲妳的絕情而受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.87,0:19:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠走海外 獲得成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.97,0:19:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當妳知道了傑拉爾天馬的真面目之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.97,0:19:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲了隱藏妳過去所犯下的罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.27,0:19:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有再一次殺掉天馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.57,0:19:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 妳爲什麽要把罪名轉嫁給善則呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.57,0:19:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是昌代的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.87,0:19:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我被捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.17,0:19:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司和丈夫就都被她奪走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.07,0:19:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她奪不走監獄裏的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.27,0:19:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想保護著公司等我丈夫回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.52,0:20:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.52,0:20:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn宋体}{\fs24}{\pos(332,465)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.27,0:20:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前沒有找到天馬的屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.27,0:20:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是他還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.47,0:20:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直爲此擔驚受怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.77,0:20:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲我也明白那首歌的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.67,0:20:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實傑拉爾在音樂會上唱這首歌的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.02,0:20:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都輕聲說一句法語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.07,0:20:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻譯成日文就是爲了挽救妳那受傷的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.07,0:20:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在重新修改的歌詞裏換了花的種類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.17,0:20:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想可能就是這個原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.77,0:20:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了紅玫瑰以外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.87,0:20:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它的分別改成了蘆荟 火炎花和橄榄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.87,0:20:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花語是悲哀 和平和光榮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.07,0:20:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.17,0:20:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬知道妳可能作爲殺人犯而被捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.67,0:21:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然懷著苦澀的回憶繼續唱這首歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.97,0:21:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還特地和加那集團簽約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.47,0:21:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.37,0:21:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然曾經一度沈浸在悲痛之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.07,0:21:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他已經不再記恨妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.87,0:21:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他自己也在事業上取得成功 非常幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.67,0:21:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想讓妳聽聽真正意義的紅色愛的夜想曲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.03,0:21:48.30,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}要用什麽方式傳達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.73,0:21:55.37,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}才能讓妳明白呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.42,0:22:04.72,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}{\fad(60,0)}自從那次之後  不知多少個季節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.37,0:22:10.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}就這樣過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.39,0:22:18.16,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}總是笑著守候在我身旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.03,0:22:28.41,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}妳不敢告訴我的事情 還有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.53,0:22:33.37,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx129}Secret of my heart  {\fscx107}{\fscy95}並不是懷疑妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.49,0:22:39.53,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}不管何時  只要還有少許的未來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.65,0:22:44.55,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}真相一定會落入手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.64,0:22:51.19,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}我無法再說什麽 只有繼續等待機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.52,0:22:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.57,0:23:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那開始就對花語入迷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.87,0:23:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 園子 ByeBye
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.07,0:23:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.97,0:23:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 路上經過花店買的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.47,0:23:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.97,0:23:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.57,0:23:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的桃花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.77,0:23:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花語是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.17,0:23:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天 下 無 敵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.77,0:23:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.67,0:23:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.87,0:23:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天下無敵是什麽意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.37,0:23:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.62,0:23:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.27,0:23:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在他們等電梯這會兒跑出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.57,0:24:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑是沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.97,0:24:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想說的是 妳是個冒充的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.07,0:24:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.17,0:24:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九個門的大搜索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.07,0:24:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.67,0:24:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉丁字母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.62,0:24:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集是在9層的高級公寓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.07,0:24:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵探團大活躍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.67,0:24:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的出場呢
